{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_lava2_set_1", "eventName": "我們都一樣", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "我們都一樣", "storyInfo": "為了瞭解身為薩卡茲的父母在維多利亞的新家過得怎麼樣，炎熔暗自觀察周圍鄰居，卻遇上了一群叫她“魔鬼”的小孩。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snowconutryinside", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.7, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.6, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$calm_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "爸爸媽媽：", "x": 180.0, "y": 170.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 1000.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n你們收到這封信的時候，我和姐姐已經在過來看你們的路上了，不用再寫信來阻攔，寫了我們也收不到的。", "x": 380.0, "y": 170.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n就算你們不肯承認，我也知道你們臨時又要搬家是什麼緣故。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n你們說戰爭已結束很久，小村又偏遠，村裡人對薩卡茲的包容度會比較高，但維多利亞真的還有那樣的地方嗎？", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n況且，倫蒂尼姆打起來之後，你們也是報喜不報憂的，所以你們現在是不是真的過得好、有沒有受到欺負，我們要來親眼確認。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n總之，有事見面聊。你們一定要照顧好自己。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2", "multi": "true", "text": "炎熔", "x": 180.0, "y": 520.0, "alignment": "right", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 800.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st2"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.6, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小炎熔，辣椒粉找到了嗎？再不醃肉，晚餐可就來不及做了……", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別催，反正他們回家之前做完不就好了。他們箱子裡的東西怎麼這麼多……", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "豎琴？我怎麼不知道他們懂音樂。", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是他們最好的朋友巴洛克先生的，好像自從戰爭開始之後，他們就沒再聯絡上他了。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……呃，怎麼還有我們小時候的作業簿！丟掉吧……", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這可不行，我們兩個常年不在家，媽媽總是會翻看的。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有什麼好看的，我們又不是不回來……還有這一大堆相簿，好！重！", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些……都是他們在倫蒂尼姆工作的時候拍的嗎？都是一些不認識的傢伙……看穿著，好像是他們的同事。每一張都保存得好完整。", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下面，全是書信。真是的，搬了那麼多次家，這些東西早該丟了吧……亂七八糟的。", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟這裡面是爸爸媽媽大半輩子的家當了……也不是一時半刻能整理完的，誰能那麼容易就把自己的人生整理清楚呢？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更何況他們白天還要出門工作……", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不在這裡，也不在這裡……架子上呢？咦……", "name": "炎熔"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……芙蓉，你看這個。", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "招聘啟事……打字員、園丁、育兒員……還都打上了叉叉。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們以前可是工程師啊……", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#4"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就算這樣也一定要住在維多利亞嗎……", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#4"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "離開了這裡，他們又能去哪裡呢？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#7$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小炎熔，把報紙放回原處去，當著他們的面可不要提起。我們……做我們做得到的事就好。", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……找不到辣椒粉，我去跟鄰居借。", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 0.9}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等——就這麼怒氣衝衝地跑出去了……還沒囑咐她千萬不能和鄰居吵架……", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#4$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_county_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你好，我住在東邊最後一棟。請問，能不能借用一點……", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……很抱歉，沒有。對不起。", "name": "鄰居A"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorclosequite"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（甚至不願意聽我說完……）", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_county_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你好，我想借用一點辣椒粉。", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorclosequite"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對方乾脆地關上了門。"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（包容……嗎？）", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_county_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$dooropenquite"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你好，我是住在……", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_243"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道。", "name": "鄰居B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_243"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個好奇的孩子從母親的身後探出頭來，偷看來訪的薩卡茲女孩。"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_243", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊爾莎，回房間去。", "name": "鄰居B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們剛搬過來不久……", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_243"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知道。你把附近鄰居的門都敲了一遍，有事嗎？", "name": "鄰居B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我姐做飯找不到辣椒粉，可以借一點嗎？", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_243"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……就為這個，請在門口稍等一下。", "name": "鄰居B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "門闔上，又輕輕打開。一顆好奇的小腦袋探出來，盯著炎熔看——具體來說，是盯著炎熔頭上的角看。"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子有點緊張地吞了口口水，猶豫許久，向炎熔伸出手來。"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "炎熔一路過來早已習慣了這樣的目光，站著沒有動。那個女孩的小手指一點點靠近，觸碰到了炎熔的衣角。"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇——是真的衣服，不是巫術變的。", "name": "好奇的孩子"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#4"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "蛤？", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#4"}, {"id": 160, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_ceramicrack"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_243"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊爾莎！你給我過來！", "name": "鄰居B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 166, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那位母親拋下了手裡的東西，衝過來將她的孩子護在身後。她臉上的神情終於不再冷靜。"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_243"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我家沒有你要的東西，你走吧。", "name": "鄰居B"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g1_victoriavillage", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "窸窸窣窣，伊爾莎從閣樓窗戶爬到屋外，興奮地向好友們打暗號。沒過多久，村子裡的人們紛紛停下腳步，遠遠觀望那詭異的場景——"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個不受歡迎的薩卡茲冷著臉走在他們的村子裡，她身後不遠處，一群小孩躡手躡腳地跟著她。"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那群小孩一下躲在灌木叢後，一下又紛紛翻滾閃身躲到樹後，互相眨眼睛、打暗號，並時不時對著手裡想像中的對講機說話。"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "報告，魔鬼已經到了湯姆家的草堆前，馬上就要走到他家門口。完畢！", "name": "伊爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_240"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "收到，城防炮已就位！", "name": "西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小朋友們，不要把彈弓對著那個人，你們這樣很危險……", "name": "擔憂的路人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_418_1#1$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一旦有成人干涉，孩子們便如羽獸般尖叫著散去，但沒過多久，便又聚集起來。"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖。你們……", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不好，魔鬼發現我們了！快撤退！", "name": "小孩們"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "魔鬼……？", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（煩人，趕快把他們嚇跑吧。）", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_firemagic", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們快看，魔鬼走過的那條路，地上有亮亮的腳印，那是什麼？", "name": "蘿絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_240"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "待著別動，我去偵察——哇哇哇，是火！魔鬼走過的路會著火！", "name": "西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看看——是真的！地上的腳印都著火了，太厲害了！", "name": "伊爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，她走遠了，快追！", "name": "蘿絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#4"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（怎麼，這樣還嚇不走你們？）", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#4"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "炎熔盯著他們手裡的彈弓看了片刻。"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哼，算了。免得傷到你們惹麻煩。來點更厲害的讓你們瞧瞧。", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#2"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈啾——", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#2"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_firemagic", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_240"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "魔鬼打噴嚏噴出火了！嗚哇，魔鬼長出火焰翅膀了！", "name": "西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 230, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇——！好……", "name": "伊爾莎&蘿絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好酷！", "name": "伊爾莎&蘿絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#3"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……還蠻有眼光嘛，小孩。", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_rhodesinpatientcenter", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1456_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（不住抽泣）", "name": "膽怯的小病人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1456_1#1$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "炎熔抓耳撓腮，摸摸口袋，想掏出點糖果哄小孩，又想起芙蓉叮囑過，孩子們需要空腹抽血。"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可惡的老姐，把自己叫過來幫忙，說什麼看到有同族在，這些剛在戰爭中失去了父母的孩子就不會那麼害怕，明明還是一直哭啊！"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "病房裡此起彼伏的哭聲使她手足無措。每一天，每一天，只要戰爭還在持續，這樣的哭聲便不會停止。"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……你們，想看煙火嗎？", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1456_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（啜泣）", "name": "膽怯的小病人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1456_1#1$1"}, {"id": 260, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我就當是想了。看仔細了，機會只有一次啊。", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳。", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 264, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#2"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "火焰啊，照耀這片大地吧！", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#2"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_firemagic", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$firemagic_explosion", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 1.2}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "xstrength": 40.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一朵火焰形成的煙火直衝天花板，在病房上空炸開。炎熔偷看那些孩子的表情。他們被火焰吸引，有那麼一瞬間忘記了哭泣。"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，火焰觸發了消防裝置，把眾人淋得狼狽不堪。病房裡的哭聲，短暫地，被笑聲取代了。"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "果然哪裡的小孩子都一樣，一點小伎倆就能騙到。"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪裡的……都一樣嗎？"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snowconutryinside", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "playmusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小炎熔，你回來了。周圍鄰居怎麼樣？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鄰居？我不是去借辣椒粉的嗎……", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 295, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "觀察了一圈，你還放心嗎？沒和別人吵起來吧？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 297, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都說我是去借辣椒粉的了。", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#1"}, {"id": 299, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小炎熔？你在找什麼？門外那些小傢伙是你新交的朋友嗎？你還是那麼會逗小朋友——", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦，帶著一大包東西……出門了？", "name": "芙蓉"}, "figure_art": "avg_1024_hbisc2_1#3$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g1_victoriavillage", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "報告，魔鬼從屋裡出來了！現在到達了小花園，完畢。", "name": "伊爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 317, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_firemagic", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_240"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇！火！我是說魔、魔鬼操縱火焰……燒斷了樹幹！報告，魔鬼在用大量的樹枝搭建一個可疑的巨大的東西。", "name": "西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼巨大的東西，說清楚！", "name": "伊爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 325, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_240"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看不懂！報告，魔鬼現在抖開了一張白色床單……不對，是白色巫術材料，將它展開在樹枝上，請求情報人員分析！", "name": "西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 331, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "情報人員到！嗯，依我看，這一定是……某種危險的祭壇。", "name": "蘿絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，以樹枝支撐帷幕，你們看，她把倒下的樹幹推過來了，那是用來放置祭品的祭品台。", "name": "蘿絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1"}, {"id": 335, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_240"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（倒吸一口氣）村子有危險！", "name": "西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 337, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_240"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（瑟縮）", "name": "西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 339, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "膽、膽小鬼！我們得看好她，保護我們的村子！", "name": "伊爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 341, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "慢著！魔鬼拿出了新東西！一種機械裝置，好像是個……投影機？不對，一定是用來施放巫術的裝置！", "name": "蘿絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1"}, {"id": 343, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_devicebeep"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "ac6_6", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話音剛落，隨著機器開啟，白色“巫術材料”上出現了一隻比高樓還巨大的、怒吼的巨獸。"}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊——！", "name": "小孩們"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.7, "r": 0.95, "g": 0.95, "b": 0.95, "fadetime": 0.02, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_sp_ballista"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.95, "g": 0.95, "b": 0.95, "fadetime": 0.25, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.6, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 8.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "轟！啪！"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“巫術材料”放映出的畫面裡，變異的巨獸瞬間將高樓大廈踐踏為齏粉，絕望的人們哭泣奔逃著，期待英雄的登場。"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "炎熔，羅德島精英幹員，法術大師，災害專家。此刻，城市的生存希望掌握在她的手中。"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快看！英雄來了！", "name": "小孩們"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_240"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦，打大怪獸的大英雄長得是不是和那個魔鬼……不對，和那個人……一模一樣？", "name": "西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g1_victoriavillage", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 378, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "炎熔大模大樣地坐在孩子們口中的“祭品台”上，做出一副舒舒服服享受電影的樣子——"}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她把這部還未上映的電影帶在身上，本是想哄哄父母開心的。"}}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "儘管她對那些硬加進去的誇張劇情表達過鄙夷，但看來整體效果還真不錯。"}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "孩子們紛紛偷看她，對比著她與電影中那位英雄的長相。"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們聽不懂炎國話，卻被電影中的特效吸引，不知不覺，他們就靠得近了一些，又近了一些，幾乎靠到了炎熔身邊。"}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g1_victoriavillage", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_1011_purgatory_1#3"}}, {"id": 393, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（哼，算你們有眼光，那就讓你們看點真東西——）", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "char_1011_purgatory_1#3"}, {"id": 394, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "糟糕，大怪獸要把房子踩扁了，英雄快逃！", "name": "伊爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_240"}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "英雄是不會逃的，你們看，她要發射火焰了！", "name": "西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 401, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿……你們兩個，她、她呢？", "name": "蘿絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊啊啊大怪獸要追上來了！", "name": "伊爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿！嘿！她、她不見啦！那個人，我們的鄰居……", "name": "蘿絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_240"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊！那個人，她剛剛還坐在這裡的，去哪裡了？", "name": "西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 409, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_firemagic", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 412, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$firemagic_explosion", "volume": 1.0, "delay": 1.2}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "炎熔原本坐著的地方不知何時已空無一人。突然，一條火焰從他們的身後襲來，射向了那塊床單做的布幕。孩子們尖叫起來。"}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我說，這……這不會真的是祭壇吧，我們被騙上來了！", "name": "蘿絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快跑……快……啊！", "name": "伊爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 421, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但孩子們卻止住了腳步，被眼前的場景驚得忘了言語。"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2050_1#1$1", "duration": 2.0}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在他們眼前的，是一位換上了戰鬥服的、英姿颯爽的女子。她帥氣而冷酷地揮手，火焰撲向了“巫術材料”，或者說，床單做成的布幕。"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "布幕上的巨獸痛苦地嚎叫著，被燒為灰燼。而後火焰熄滅，沒有傷到周圍的花草半分。"}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇——", "name": "小孩們"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2050_1#1$1"}, {"id": 429, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好厲害啊！英雄，你真的打過大怪獸嗎？", "name": "伊爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_240"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛才那招，能不能教我？", "name": "西奧"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_240"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你的戰鬥服真好看，我是說，真帥！", "name": "蘿絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_700_1#1$1"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "英雄英雄，我先問的，先回答我——啊！……媽媽？", "name": "伊爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 437, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當電影在火焰中落幕，孩子們才察覺到自己的家長早已在不遠處緊張地盯著他們。家長們上前，不由分說地將他們的孩子往家裡拉。"}}, {"id": 440, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_243"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "伊爾莎，跟你說過不准偷跑出來的，你今晚好好在房間裡反省。", "name": "伊爾莎的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 442, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別拉我啊媽媽，我跟你說，剛才我看到了很厲害的……", "name": "伊爾莎"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_661_1#1$1"}, {"id": 444, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_243"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不許說了。", "name": "伊爾莎的母親"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_243"}, {"id": 446, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2050_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2050_1#1$1"}, {"id": 448, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2050_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跑這麼快，我又不比你們多一對獠牙、一雙翅膀……", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2050_1#1$1"}, {"id": 450, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2050_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算了，跑光了也就清淨了。省得哄小孩子，吵吵鬧鬧煩死人。", "name": "炎熔"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2050_1#1$1"}, {"id": 452, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 453, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 455, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是……？", "name": "炎熔"}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "炎熔"}}, {"id": 457, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 458, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 459, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在伊爾莎原本坐著的地方，靜靜地放著一瓶辣椒粉。炎熔愣了片刻，想抬頭喊出感謝，但那些人早已走得不見了蹤影。"}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是，她收拾起東西往家裡走，腳步輕鬆了一些。"}}, {"id": 461, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 463, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 465, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 466, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 467, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 468, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 469, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}